{"tid":1992654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"反修例事件28宗公務員懷疑貪污案　26宗涉及警員","createTime":"2020-04-28T09:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T12:01:28.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"80d69e6fcacf84722b5fd5a7103f02d32748329a","tid":1992654,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"廉政公署表示，截至今年2月底，正處理28宗反修例事件中涉及公務員的懷疑貪污個案，其中26宗涉及警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n廉政公署回覆民主黨議員林卓廷，於立法會特別財委會的查詢，指目前28宗於反修例事件中涉及公務員的懷疑貪污個案之中，有26宗涉及警務人員。林卓廷要求廉政公署交代涉及的警員人數。<br />\n<br />\n廉署表示，基於保密原則，廉政公署不適宜透露個案資料，包括涉案警務人員的數目。"},{"pid":"a5304b3bb6ae10cdd6a3ba1f6695bdb85bf0b36f","tid":1992654,"uid":21545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da88fec308932752108ecbe7680f922536bfb28","tid":1992654,"uid":25797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"咪又係同柒婆負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18647f7b5c369662c219e56bd8a7b6ae056cf56d","tid":1992654,"uid":120188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪真係污糟辣撻"},{"pid":"f5761413cbfdf24205bf94dcea40afc74e4b8876","tid":1992654,"uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a5304b3bb6ae10cdd6a3ba1f6695bdb85bf0b36f","tid":1992654,"uid":21545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"26宗, 如果每宗10個都260個<br />\n我就真係唔明點解保密原則可以透露26宗但唔可以透露人數"},{"pid":"c4fa22f5462925ed122b43bbb2ab4db55a2743b0","tid":1992654,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"除咗721，邊件事可以貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caff9131c28d99fdd194f358ff7092383c462cf1","tid"